text: > Top News Is the SEC down? League depth a question at midway point FILE -= In this Oct. 17, 2015, file photo, Alabama head coach Nick Saban, center, waves to fans as he runs off the field following an NCAA college football game against Texas A&M in College Station, Texas. Alabama and LSU certainly look like teams that could make some postseason noise. Which one could be decided after they meet on Nov. 7. (AP Photo/Eric Gay, File)
